text = "IMPORTANT, 
if you have not played the tutorial yet, press the \"play\" button in the main menu and then press \"tutorial\".
This manual is designed to help if you needed more details than what the tutorial game mode provides."
horizontal_alignment = 1
vertical_alignment = 1

